  "text": "Creating good quality cooking recipes is an ancient art that has been developed by a wide variety of cultures. Nowadays, technology and modelling bring us new tools to experiment and test cooking recipes. Some solutions that have been studied are synthesizing cooking recipes using video [CITATION_1] or recommend cooking recipes based on preferences of a user [CITATION_2] . But a few solutions tackle the problem of generating an optimal cooking recipe based on an input space of ingredients, tools and other criteria.",
